title: 820-00165 Missing PP1V05 S0
message:
I have a water damaged macbook air that has been repaired to the extent that I'm just missing PP1V05 S0. I dont have an oscilloscope to see if PCH HSIO PWR EN is present. No water damage was near u8005. 

PP3V3 S0 = 3.324
pp1v5_s0 = 1.508
PP1V05 S0 = 0.064
PP1V05 S0SW PCH HSIO = 0.062

Any help would be appreciated, thank you.

title: 820-00165 Missing PP1V05 S0
message: 1V05 is generated by U7600, check voltages around there.
